Products.RichDescription:
MAGNUM LUXE ICE CREAM RUBY RASPBERRY 360 ML
INTRODUCING THE NEW MAGNUM RUBY

After Dark, Milk and White chocolate; Ruby is the most extraordinary chocolate discovery in the last 80 years.
Ruby, as 4th type of chocolate, is carefully made with selected Ruby cocoa beans and gets its exceptional natural color and berry taste from them, without adding any colorants or fruit flavorings.
The newly discovered Ruby Chocolate meets ice cream for the first time with Magnum, offering Pleasure Seekers the opportunity to indulge in an authentic Ruby experience. A decadent union of thick cracking Ruby Chocolate, indulgent velvety ice cream and a luscious raspberry swirl to create a superior pleasure experience. Dream away in the intensive refreshing sensation of fruity sourness and the creamy mouthfeel of this Ruby Chocolate experience.
Expertly crafted by master chocolatiers, Magnum uses only the highest quality ingredients and responsibly sourced cocoa beans. Magnum Ruby is available as a stick. The first of its kind, it is innovatively made with unique and rare Ruby cacao beans.
Indulge in a beautifully rich ice cream experience and reclaim those precious moments of pleasure.

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected by Rainforest Alliance Certified™ farmers. Magnum cocoa beans have a long way to go before they become Magnum chocolate. We’re working closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure all our cocoa beans are responsibly sourced to produce our icecreams, sticks and tubs, in every flavour, with the best chocolate quality. It’s about quality and sustainability throughout every step of the journey. Every Magnum stick, every Magnum tub represent the perfect, indulgent and delicious treat or snack for any family. Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum, and we have been taking pleasure very seriously. Thick Chocolate. Premium ingrediants. Unique flavours. Smooth ice cream. The perfect balance. To us, pleasure is everything. The pleasure of each individual and their freedom to experience it genuinely and in full. We know pleasure can be found in both the smallest and the biggest things. But only if you are brave enough will you really find your pleasure, your true pleasure that stays with you. We are Magnum, the champions of true pleasure..

Caramel Ego has now elevated to Magnum LUXE, the most decadent and indulgent Magnum range yet. MAGNUM LUXE ICE CREAM GOLD CARAMELISED CHOCOLATE MP4 360 ML

Magnum LUXE is the first super premium ice cream, positioned at the top of the range of indulgent ice cream sticks and tubs - a permissable luxury

Each of the flavors are also extremely decadent, have you already tried Raspberry Panna Cotta sticks and Salted Caramel pint?
For the first time, the Magnum LUXE range features layers of velvety ice cream, luscious sauces and thick chocolate, paired together for the perfect balance to transport you to experience an indulgent moment of pleasure.
This Magnum is a true authentic pleasure, so good it’s worth letting go for. When indulging in Magnum LUXE you should feel as though you are having an extra special treat and spoiling yourself!

We’re working closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure all our cocoa beans are responsibly sourced (and delicious, of course!). It’s about quality and sustainability throughout every step of the journey. Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum icecream, and we have been taking pleasure very seriously. Thick Chocolate. Smooth ice cream. The perfect balance. To us, pleasure is everything. The pleasure of each individual and their freedom to experience it genuinely and in full. We know pleasure can be found in both the smallest and the biggest things. Can be a treat, a stick, a tub, a bar, a snack, a dessert. But only if you are brave enough will you really find your pleasure, your true pleasure that stays with you. We are Magnum ice cream, the champions of true pleasure.
